## 22. Coding Patterns สำคัญ

### Styled Components Pattern:
```javascript
import styled from 'styled-components';

const Container = styled.View`
  flex: 1;
  background-color: ${({theme: t}) => t.COLORS.WHITE_1};
`;

const Title = styled.Text`
  font-family: ${({theme: t}) => t.FONT_FAMILY.TH.BOLD};
  font-size: ${({theme: t}) => t.FONT_SIZE.SIZE_18}px;
  color: ${({theme: t}) => t.COLORS.BLACK_1};
`;
```

### Component Pattern:
```javascript
import React, {useState, useCallback} from 'react';
import {useNavigation} from '@react-navigation/native';
import {ROUTE_PATH} from '../../assets';
import {ButtonApp, Headers} from '../../components';
import i18n from '../../utils/i18n';

const ScreenName = () => {
  const navigation = useNavigation();
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  return (
    <Container>
      <Headers title={i18n.t('screen.title')} />
    </Container>
  );
};

export default ScreenName;
```

### Import Order:
1. React / React Native
2. Third-party libraries
3. Assets (theme, constants, locales)
4. Components
5. Widgets
6. Store (actions, reducers)
7. Helpers / Utils
8. Local (Section/, sub-components)

